    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
      <p>This collection contains correspondence, accounts,
         speeches, essays, poems, plays, and a day book. Other items
         include invitations, calling cards, class notes, legal
         documents a few miscellaneous items.</p>
